OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fdry evening for most with some late
OL,7,Fsunshine, but with cloud along the
OL,8,Fcoasts. Cloud builds inland overnight
OL,9,Fwith patchy coastal drizzle possible.
OL,10,FLight northerly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy with patchy drizzle
OL,13,Fpossible through the morning. Sunny
OL,14,Fspells developing through the
OL,15,Fafternoon and into the evening. Light
OL,16,Fto moderate northerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
